Congress has no business reauthorizing FISA 702 without a warrant requirement for citizens.

No more spying on Americans. https://t.co/1qyIZbRhEw

Our own government shouldn’t be conducting secret political spying on lawmakers…

OR ANY AMERICANS. https://t.co/GvyWUu0KWH
A majority of both Republican AND Democrat voters agree! https://t.co/4Cxv0ThK2z
Republicans support school choice so that all students can escape the systems Democrats broke. https://t.co/T8TkCfoOIL

Now imagine if we enforced our ban on them voting.

Do you see why Democrats in Congress are against this? https://t.co/GLWUI6Ebk7

The SAVE Act’s goal is to require proof of citizenship to register and ID to vote in federal elections, commonsense security measures supported by a majority of Democrats and Republicans across America.

The Swamp’s goal is to lie about it. https://t.co/90mrrz8K03
I’m putting it on there. https://t.co/42xMPgWhgh

Thrilled that [this surprisingly economic policy-minded version of] Bad Bunny wants to get rid of the Jones Act, and I look forward to his upcoming song, “Vote a favor de la Ley de Aguas Abiertas de Mike Lee.” https://t.co/Ty9nvP7I1M
